CustomField.description: It is a unique registration code assigned to the registrant. The DDTC registration code consist of a letter prefix, M (assigned to a manufacturer and/or exporter) or K (assigned to a broker), followed by four or five digits (e.g. K-1234 or M12345)

CustomField.label: Registration Number
